prompt.title: Embedding for AI Reshapes Human-Computer Interaction
prompt.content: Large language models, such as GPT and Claude, are identified as the key technological drivers behind this transformation in human-computer interaction. This advancement is compared to the role that Moore's Law and microprocessor improvements played in previous generations of programming languages.
